OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FSunny
OL,6,Fspells and showers Monday. Dry start
OL,7,FTuesday with rain possible later in
OL,8,Fwest. Mostly cloudy with outbreaks of
OL,9,Frain on Wednesday. Winds light Monday
OL,10,Fthen breezy Tuesday and Wednesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
